CREATE TABLE "TESTUSER01"."SALES" 
   (	"USERGENDER" VARCHAR2(4000) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP", 
	"USERCITY" VARCHAR2(4000) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP", 
	"USERSENTIMENT" NUMBER, 
	"ZIPCODE" VARCHAR2(4000) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP", 
	"SKU" VARCHAR2(4000) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP", 
	"CREATEDATE" VARCHAR2(64) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP" NOT NULL ENABLE, 
	"CATEGORY" VARCHAR2(4000) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP", 
	"PRICE" NUMBER(12,5), 
	"COUNTRY" VARCHAR2(4000) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP", 
	"COUNTRYCODE" VARCHAR2(4000) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP", 
	"USERSTATE" VARCHAR2(4000) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP", 
	"CATEGORYGROUP" VARCHAR2(4000) COLLATE "USING_NLS_COMP", 
	 PRIMARY KEY ("CREATEDATE")
  USING INDEX  ENABLE, 
	 SUPPLEMENTAL LOG DATA (ALL) COLUMNS
   )  DEFAULT COLLATION "USING_NLS_COMP" ;
